{"tid":1410443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［被罷工］今日塞地鐵好成功","createTime":"2019-08-05T01:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T02:58:07.000Z","uid":200021,"like":333,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c95f8edf50b547a6226f72b99e61d873c1952e","tid":1410443,"uid":200021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:35:50.000Z","msg":"今朝已經遲咗起身 慢慢咁出門<br />\n出咗門無耐 公司有人問會唔會有人要遲到<br />\n我答咗應該會遲少少到<br />\n無幾耐老細就話今日因交通問題可以唔使返<br />\n作為香港人就梗係要食住嗰勢罷工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連埋我已經有幾個被罷工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝你地 各位一陣見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 見到九龍塘塞到咁好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569c5b52f656a90f6b77b2f04a5bae84b7dcc79f","tid":1410443,"uid":74182,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:36:26.000Z","msg":"其實日日塞都諗得過"},{"pid":"0a02db1bd5fa046196411755d4b67f6e29c4b1c8","tid":1410443,"uid":200021,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"569c5b52f656a90f6b77b2f04a5bae84b7dcc79f","tid":1410443,"uid":74182,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:36:26.000Z","msg":"其實日日塞都諗得過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:37:38.000Z","msg":"反正撐你嘅點都係撐你架啦<br />\n老細罵咪話 咁我被罷工都唔想架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307d61cb20df17b519c79b8891ab6afdd4d9b6cf","tid":1410443,"uid":54181,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:38:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a07f7984c9e09bc293ddcb529e8262076210e9c","tid":1410443,"uid":45376,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:38:27.000Z","msg":"但主要幹道冇塞到<br />\n唔係鐵路沿線嘅被霸工失敗<br />\n呢啲位要檢討下點搞"},{"pid":"801aa2bf539bc3e2317687f60db878443d24a6ce","tid":1410443,"uid":134059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a1c95f8edf50b547a6226f72b99e61d873c1952e","tid":1410443,"uid":200021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:35:50.000Z","msg":"今朝已經遲咗起身 慢慢咁出門<br />\n出咗門無耐 公司有人問會唔會有人要遲到<br />\n我答咗應該會遲少少到<br />\n無幾耐老細就話今日因交通問題可以唔使返<br />\n作為香港人就梗係要食住嗰勢罷工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連埋我已經有幾個被罷工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝你地 各位一陣見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 見到九龍塘塞到咁好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:38:55.000Z","msg":"你老細咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2951b911fbcd560fb46d0cddfe9af87c8eb096d6","tid":1410443,"uid":226955,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:39:02.000Z","msg":"喺堵塞交通呢件事上面，大家要避免陷入群眾鬥群眾嘅陷阱，可能之後開始會有（犬儒/ 廢老/ 五毛）會吹風話示威者今次真係擾到民，鬧示威者喺度搞三搞四，但係請大家諗深一層，係啲乜嘢原因令到班示威者要咁樣做？<br />\n<br />\n歸根究底係政府冇回應五大訴求呀，警察開槍射頭，虐打手無寸鐵示威者，放任埋黑社會周街打人放煙花，警察仲要同黑社會有講有笑呀，催淚彈放題、開槍打頭、唔比食藥，已經有好幾個義士暈低咗未醒返，又有少女比黑警除曬底褲，將少女私處暴露喺眾人面前，如此劣行同當年日本皇軍有乜嘢分別？<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可，大家如果要指責，請向政府指責，因為政府冇回應到五大訴求，責任在於政府，而唔係好似呢幅漫畫「某文化」咁，反而指責為人民向奴隸主抗爭嘅示威者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saa7Rku.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsaa7Rku.png&h=58898183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fcc79197ae35fadf192a4d149727ac3d63cb4b3","tid":1410443,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:39:09.000Z","msg":"爽呀 今日做得太好啦<br />\n下次再接再厲"},{"pid":"200b0854655733edd7b4b386f26c590a020cc13c","tid":1410443,"uid":43663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:40:01.000Z","msg":"我想去金鐘集會都去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daadda452f457b7c6ce494ebf8c06cd